{{Navbox
|name = Date templates

|group1 = {{tl|Currentdate}}
|list1 = Time, day of week, and date in MDY format and time zone
|group2 = {{tl|Date}}
|list2 = Date in chosen format
|group3 = {{tl|DATE}}
|list3 = Month and year, prefixed by "date=" (for use with templates through substitution)
|group4 = {{tl|Now}}
|list4 = Same as <nowiki>{{Currentdate}}</nowiki> but in a sentence
|group5 = {{tl|Plain now}}
|list5 = Date in DMY format, and time
|group6 = {{tl|Right now}}
|list6 = Blue banner with time and current number of Wikipedia articles
|group7 = {{tl|Right now (User message)}}
|list7 = Orange banner with time and current number of Wikipedia articles
|group8 = {{tl|TODAY}}
|list8 = Date in DMY
}}<noinclude>
{{doc|content=
==Usage==
This template is intended to provide a consistent "See also" for templates with "date" and "now" related titles.

==See also==
*[[Wikipedia:Age calculation templates]]
*{{tl|Start date}}
[[Category:Navigational boxes]]
[[Category:Related-topic templates]]
}}
</noinclude>

