{{col-begin}}
{{col-break}}
{{align|right|[{{edit|Template:Date and time templates}}]}}
{{col-end}}
{{col-begin}}
{{col-break}}
* {{tl|TODAY}} &ndash; Date in DMY 
* {{tl|Currentdate}} &ndash; Time, day of week, and date in MDY format
** {{tl|Now}} &ndash; Same as <nowiki>{{Currentdate}}</nowiki> but in a sentence
* {{tl|Date}} &ndash; Date in chosen format '''(Has ajustable inputs)'''
{{col-break}} <!-- make sure it's in the centre of the page -->
* {{tl|DATE}} &ndash; Month and year, prefixed by "date=" (for use with templates through substitution)
* {{tl|Right now}} &ndash; Blue banner with time and current number of Wikipedia articles 
** {{tl|Right now (User message)}} &ndash; Orange banner with time and current number of Wikipedia articles 
* {{tl|Plain now}} &ndash; Date in DMY format, and time 
{{col-end}}
----
{{col-begin}}
{{col-break}}
'''<u>Minute</u>'''
* {{tl|CURRENTMINUTE}}
{{col-break}}
'''<u>Hour</u>'''
* {{tl|Currenthour}}
{{col-break}}
'''<u>Week</u>'''
* {{tl|CURRENTWEEKOFYEAR}}
* {{tl|CURRENTWEEKOFMONTH}}
{{col-break}}
'''Day of Week'''
* {{tl|WEEKDAYNAME}}
